                <div class="award-content text-center">
                    <p class="section-desc pb-3">Founded in 2009, DiceBoyScripts’s public platform is used by nearly everyone who codes to learn, share their knowledge, collaborate, and build their careers. Our products and tools help developers and technologists in life and at work. These products include
                        <a href="#" class="text-color hover-underline">DiceBoyScripts for Teams</a>, <a href="#" class="text-color hover-underline">DiceBoyScripts Advertising</a>, and DiceBoyScripts for
                        <a href="#" class="text-color hover-underline">Talent</a> and <a href="#" class="text-color hover-underline">Jobs</a>.</p>
                    <p class="section-desc pb-3">DiceBoyScripts for Teams, our core SaaS collaboration product, is helping thousands of companies around the world as the transition to remote work, address business continuity challenges, and undergo digital transformation.</p>
                    <p class="section-desc pb-3">Whether it’s on DiceBoyScripts or within DiceBoyScripts for Teams, community is at the center of all that we do.</p>
